William Shakespeare's A Midsummer Night's Dream;;60;;67;;PG-13;;This version of the renowned comedic play finds the world of humans intersecting with the realm of magic. The lovely Hermia (Anna Friel) is to wed Demetrius (Christian Bale), but she truly cares for Lysander (Dominic West). Hermia's friend, Helena (Calista Flockhart), is in love with Demetrius, while other romantic entanglements abound in the woods, with married fairy rulers Titania (Michelle Pfeiffer) and Oberon (Rupert Everett) toying with various lovers and each other.;;Comedy;;Michael Hoffman;;1999;;Kevin Kline,Michelle Pfeiffer,Rupert Everett,Stanley Tucci,Calista Flockhart,Anna Friel,Christian Bale,Dominic West,David Strathairn,Sophie Marceau,Roger Rees,Bernard Hill,Bill Irwin,Sam Rockwell,Max Wright,Gregory Jbara,John Sessions,Deirdre Harrison,Heather Parisi,Annalisa Cordone;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1090918-midsummer_nights_dream